  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-04-19",
    "date": "2021-09-15T21:14:11Z",
    "text": "Saving Hypodermic Injections and Offering vaccines to Taxpayers Swiftly Act of 2021 or the SHOTS Act of 2021\n\nThis bill prohibits any alien who is not a lawful permanent resident from receiving a COVID-19 vaccine until the earlier of (1) the date when all U.S. nationals and lawful permanent residents who wish to receive a vaccine have been fully vaccinated, or (2) December 31, 2021."
  },
